response.original_title: Hello Kitty et ses amis. La cuisine des petits chefs
response.overview: Hello Kitty and her friends show us the cuisine of the world. Disguised as little local chefs, they take us to Italy with its famous Neapolitan pizza, Japan with its sushi, and to the United States with its delicious apple pie. You too can come and take a trip around the world of cuisine with Hello Kitty and her friends!
response.title: Hello Kitty and Friends: Little Chefs' Kitchen
